name: France Fan Token
description: France Fan Token born by the worldwide community of France National team fans. Bringing people closer together. Own $FRA to have the opportunity to receive special offers such as VIP tickets when the French team competes.Our team with a strong affection for the French national team. Hoping to make $FRA popular with everyone in the crypto market. With the goal of getting $FRA to grow to 10,000, even 100,000 holders. We donate the money to support the fans of the French team and support youth football foundations around the world. With the desire to spread the love of the French team to everyone.
